<title>tʿạly̱ yạ yswʿ bytnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- tʿạly̱ yạ yswʿ bytnạ .. wạmlạ ḥyạtnạ ṣlạẗ
 wbạrk ʿyltnạ .. wạdynạ ạ̉ḥly̱ ḥyạẗ
 1- (bmḥbtk ḥwạlynạ .. qrbnạ mn bʿḍynạ
 wkl wạḥd fynạ .. tmlk bạlḥb ʿlyh)2
 2- (nʿbdk yạ ạ̹lhnạ .. fy bytnạ ạ̹nt mlknạ
 wklmtk fy ḥyạtnạ .. ạ̉sạs bnrjʿ lyh)2
 3- (ḥyạtnạ tbqy̱ sẖhạdẗ .. kl ywm zyạdẗ
 wạmlạ qlwbnạ ạ̹rạdẗ .. nʿrf ạlnạs byk)2</lyrics>
</song>